g src=3D"https://statistics.laerd.com/spss-tutorials/img/mr/lr-20-regressio=
n-menu.png" data-src=3D"img/mr/lr-20-regression-menu.png" alt=3D"Menu for a=
 multiple regression analysis in SPSS Statistics" width=3D"100%"><p>Publish=
ed with written permission from SPSS Statistics, IBM Corporation.</p>
			</div>
	<p class=3D"note"><span class=3D"note-title">Note:</span> Don't worry that=
 you're selecting <strong><u>A</u>nalyze &gt; <u>R</u>egression &gt; <u>L</=
u>inear...</strong> on the main menu or that the dialogue boxes in the step=
