t=3D"Enter" width=3D"85" height=3D"22"> method is the name given by SPSS St=
atistics to standard regression analysis.</p>
	</li>
=09
	<li>Click on the <img class=3D"spss-image-in-text" src=3D"https://statisti=
cs.laerd.com/spss-tutorials/img/mr/statistics-button.png" data-src=3D"img/m=
r/statistics-button.png" alt=3D"Statistics" width=3D"71" height=3D"24"> but=
ton. You will be presented with the <strong>Linear Regression: Statistics</=
strong> dialogue box, as shown below:
	<div class=3D"spss-image" style=3D"max-width:374px;max-height: 366px;"><im=
g src=3D"https://statistics.laerd.com/spss-tutorials/img/mr/lr-20-statistic=
