 src=3D"https://statistics.laerd.com/spss-tutorials/img/mr/mr-statistics-se=
lected.png" data-src=3D"img/mr/mr-statistics-selected.png" alt=3D"'Linear R=
egression: Statistics' dialogue box. Multiple regression analysis in SPSS. =
'Confidence intervals' option selected" width=3D"100%"><p>Published with wr=
itten permission from SPSS Statistics, IBM Corporation.</p>
			</div>
	</li>
=09
	<li>Click on the <img class=3D"spss-image-in-text" src=3D"https://statisti=
